<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Anthropic Alignment Research — Reading List</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #faf8f3;
    --card: #ffffff;
    --ink: #1a1a1a;
    --muted: #6b6960;
    --rule: #e3dfd5;
    --accent: #6e1923;
    --accent-soft: #f4ebec;
    --done: #4a6b3a;
    --done-soft: #ecf2e6;
    --code-bg: #f1ede5;
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    :root {
      --bg: #1a1816;
      --card: #232120;
      --ink: #ebe8e0;
      --muted: #8d8a82;
      --rule: #383532;
      --accent: #c97a82;
      --accent-soft: #2c1f21;
      --done: #8db573;
      --done-soft: #1e2a18;
      --code-bg: #2a2825;
    }
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; }
  body {
    font-family: Charter, 'Iowan Old Style', 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: var(--bg);
    margin: 0;
    padding: 2rem 1rem 4rem;
  }
  .page {
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  header {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.1rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .subtitle {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .lede {
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .progress-wrap {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .progress-stat {
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
  }
  .progress-stat strong {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .progress-bar {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 180px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--rule);
    border-radius: 3px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }
  .progress-bar::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: var(--pct, 0%);
    background: var(--done);
    transition: width 0.3s ease;
  }
  .reset-btn {
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
  }
  .reset-btn:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }
  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 0.3rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .section-meta {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .entry {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
    transition: border-color 0.15s ease;
  }
  .entry.done {
    border-color: var(--done);
    background: var(--done-soft);
  }
  .entry-head {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    padding: 0.9rem 1.1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .entry-check {
    margin-top: 0.32rem;
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    accent-color: var(--done);
    cursor: pointer;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .entry-body {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .entry-title {
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.35;
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
  }
  .entry-title a {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--muted);
  }
  .entry-title a:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
    border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
  }
  .entry.done .entry-title a {
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .entry-meta {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .entry-meta .year {
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }
  .entry-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    padding: 0.1rem 0.5rem;
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    color: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-left: 0.4rem;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }
  .entry-tag.code { background: var(--code-bg); color: var(--muted); }
  .entry-actions {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 0.4rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .toggle-notes {
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    font-family: inherit;
    color: var(--muted);
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-style: dotted;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
  .toggle-notes:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  .checked-date {
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .notes {
    display: none;
    padding: 0 1.1rem 1rem 3.2rem;
  }
  .notes.open { display: block; }
  .notes textarea {
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 80px;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: var(--bg);
    resize: vertical;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .notes textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }
  footer {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  footer code {
    font-style: normal;
    background: var(--code-bg);
    padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-size: 0.92em;
  }
  @media print {
    body { background: white; padding: 1rem; }
    .progress-wrap, .toggle-notes, .reset-btn { display: none; }
    .notes { display: block !important; }
    .entry { break-inside: avoid; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

<header>
  <h1>Anthropic Alignment Research</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">A reading list for the dictatorship-of-AI essay project</p>
  <p class="lede">
    Twenty-five primary sources from Anthropic's research and policy publications,
    covering Constitutional AI, sycophancy, agentic misalignment, alignment faking,
    foundational alignment work, and overall safety agenda. Check items as you read;
    progress and notes are saved locally in your browser.
  </p>
</header>

<div class="progress-wrap">
  <div class="progress-stat">
    <strong id="done-count">0</strong> of <strong id="total-count">25</strong> read
  </div>
  <div class="progress-bar" id="progress-bar"></div>
  <div class="progress-stat" id="pct-display">0%</div>
  <button class="reset-btn" id="reset-btn">Reset all</button>
</div>

<section>
  <h2>1. Constitutional AI &amp; Claude's Constitution</h2>
  <p class="section-meta">The foundational technique and its evolving public document — start here for the Anthropic alignment ethos.</p>

